---
title: "AAR-0002: Autonomous Consolidation"
type: task
project: autonomous-agent-research
project-code: AAR
task-id: AAR-0002
priority: P1
status: pending
effort: low
created: 2026-04-07
author: mccall
depends-on: [AAR-0001]
blocks: [AAR-0003, AAR-0004, AAR-0005]
files-modified: [src/libs/reflect.ts, src/tools/consolidate-memory.ts]
files-created: []
