---
title: "AAR-0004: LLM Judge Panel"
type: task
project: autonomous-agent-research
project-code: AAR
task-id: AAR-0004
priority: P2
status: pending
effort: medium
created: 2026-04-07
author: mccall
depends-on: [AAR-0002]
blocks: [AAR-0006]
files-created: [src/libs/judge-panel.ts]
files-modified: []
