bun build src/libs/gates.ts --target bun > /dev/null
bun build src/libs/autonomous-distill.ts --target bun > /dev/null
```

Then from main after merge, I'll run `bun run tool autonomous-distill --agent tala` to verify proposals now pass Gate 3.

## Constraints

- DO NOT change the 3-line limit (this is an additive fix, not a relaxation of the line count)
- DO NOT change the 1-removal limit
- DO NOT modify any other gate (safety, drift, regression, constitution stay as-is)
- DO NOT modify distill-soul.ts (this fix is purely on the gate/apply side)
- Commit with a clear message explaining the fix

